"How to Throw a Ball" - Interactive Mobility Game 

Description: 
An interactive game that includes levels and a point system. This game is intended to help people with mobility issues, 
encouraging people to exercise their arm and finger joints.

Design Process:
The coloring, game mechanics and design of the game was something I came up with and established within the project. 
The coding components were provided by groupwork basic skills, as well as help from TA's and instructors. 

How to play:
https://editor.p5js.org/mlspark2/full/tjWwZBm0L
